quran[26{c,v,t}:
53,1,tarre ki qasam jab gayab honay lagey
53,2,ke tumahray Rafeeq ( Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) nah rasta bhoolay hain nah bhatkay hain
53,3,aur nah khwahish nafs se munh se baat nikaltay hain
53,4,yeh ( quran ) to hukum khuda hai jo ( un ki taraf ) bheja jata hai
53,5,un ko nihayat qowat walay ne sikhaya
53,6,( yani Jibraiel ) taaqatwar ne phir woh poooray nazar aeye
53,7,aur woh ( aasman ke ) ounchay kinare mein they
53,8,phir qareeb hue aur aur agay barhay
53,9,to do kamaan ke faaslay par ya is se bhi kam
53,10,phir khuda ne apne bande ki taraf jo bheja so bheja
53,11,jo kuch unhon ne dekha un ke dil ne is ko jhoot nah maana
53,12,kiya jo kuch woh dekhte hain tum is mein un se jhagarte ho ?
53,13,aur unhon ne is ko aik baar bhi dekha hai
53,14,parli hadd ki berri ke paas
53,15,isi ke paas rehne ki jannat hai
53,16,jab ke is berry par chhaa raha tha jo chhaa raha tha
53,17,un ki aankhh nah to aur taraf mael hui aur nah ( hadd se ) agay barhi
53,18,unhon ne apne perwar-digaar ( ki qudrat ) ki kitni hi barri barri nishanain dekhen
53,19,bhala tum logon ne laat aur uzzaa ko dekha
53,20,aur teesray menat ko ( ke yeh buut kahin khuda ho saktay hain )
53,21,( mushrako! )kiya tumahray liye to betay aur khuda ke liye betiyan
53,22,yeh taqseem to bohat be insafi ki hai
53,23,woh to sirf naam hi naam hain jo tum ne aur tumahray baap dada ne ghurr liye hain. khuda ne to un ki koi sanad nazil nahi ki. yeh log mehez zan ( fasid ) aur khwahisaat nafs ke peechay chal rahay hain. halaank un ke perwar-digaar ki taraf se un ke paas hadaayat aa chuki hai
53,24,kiya jis cheez ki ensaan arzoo karta hai woh usay zaroor millti hai
53,25,akhirat aur duniya to allah hi ke haath mein hai
53,26,aur asmano mein bohat se farishtay hain jin ki sifarish kuch bhi faida nahi deti magar is waqt ke khuda jis ke liye chahay ijazat bakhshay aur ( sifarish ) pasand kere
